The Upside of Anger;;63;;75;;R;;After her husband runs off with his secretary, Terry Wolfmeyer (Joan Allen) is left to fend for herself -- and her four daughters (Keri Russell, Evan Rachel Wood, Erika Christensen, Alicia Witt). As she hits rock bottom, Terry finds a friend and drinking buddy in next-door neighbor Denny (Kevin Costner), a former baseball player. As the two grow closer, and her daughters increasingly rely on Denny, Terry starts to have reservations about where their relationship is headed.;;Drama,Comedy,Romance;;Mike Binder;;2005;;Joan Allen,Kevin Costner,Erika Christensen,Evan Rachel Wood,Keri Russell,Alicia Witt,Mike Binder,Dane Christensen,Tom Harper,Danny Webb,Magdalena Manville,Suzanne Bertish,David Firth;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/upside_of_anger